sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / kubectl
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Webhook as KServe Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Controller as KServe Controller<br/>Manager
    participant Storage as S3 / GCS / Azure<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant StorageInit as Storage Initializer<br/>Init Container
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Istio Gateway /<br/>OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Predictor as Predictor Pod<br/>8080/TCP HTTP

    Note over User, Predictor: Flow 1: InferenceService Model Deployment (RawDeployment)

    User->>K8sAPI: Create InferenceService CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / cert
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Mutate/Validate<br/>mTLS (API server cert)
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admission Response
    K8sAPI-->>User: InferenceService created

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Watch InferenceService<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: InferenceService event

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Deployment + Service<br/>+ HPA + VirtualService/HTTPRoute
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Resources created

    StorageInit->>Storage: Download model artifacts<br/>Auth: Storage credentials
    Storage-->>StorageInit: Model artifacts

    Note over Client, Predictor: Flow 1 continued: Inference Request

    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/models/{model}:predict<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Configurable
    Gateway->>Predictor: Forward request<br/>HTTP / mTLS (Istio)
    Predictor-->>Gateway: Prediction response
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON response

    Note over User, Predictor: Flow 2: LLMInferenceService Request Routing

    participant LLMClient as LLM Client
    participant GW as Gateway<br/>HTTPRoute<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Scheduler as llm-d Scheduler<br/>9002/TCP gRPC
    participant LLMPod as LLM Workload Pod<br/>8000/TCP HTTPS<br/>self-signed TLS

    LLMClient->>GW: Inference request<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    GW->>Scheduler: ExtProc routing<br/>gRPC 9002/TCP<br/>TLS (configurable)
    Scheduler->>LLMPod: Routed request<br/>HTTPS 8000/TCP<br/>self-signed TLS
    LLMPod-->>Scheduler: LLM response
    Scheduler-->>GW: Response
    GW-->>LLMClient: JSON response

    Note over User, Predictor: Flow 3: Webhook Admission

    participant APIServer as kube-apiserver
    participant WebhookSvc as kserve-webhook-server<br/>443→9443/TCP HTTPS

    APIServer->>WebhookSvc: Admission request<br/>HTTPS TLS (service-ca)<br/>Auth: mTLS
    WebhookSvc->>K8sAPI: Validate resources<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>WebhookSvc: Validation result
    WebhookSvc-->>APIServer: Admission response
